comments: Jones (WAS) brushes Siakam's (TOR) right side and marginal contact occurs as Siakam dribbles in transition.
Siakam (TOR) brings both hands to the ball and resumes his dribble.
Schroder (TOR) places his hand momentarily on Jones' (WAS) hip and he immediately removes his hand as marginal contact occurs.
Flynn (TOR) steps slightly forward towards Poole (WAS) and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Siakam (TOR) and Avdija (WAS) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding.
Boucher (TOR) establishes himself in Kuzma's (WAS) path and does not deliver illegal contact as he sets the pick.
Poole (WAS) brings both hands toward Barnes' (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Kuzma (WAS) maintains verticality and absorbs the contact from Barnes (TOR) as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Schroder (TOR) briefly grasps Jones' (WAS) right wrist and quickly releases him as Jones brings both hands to the ball.
Siakam (TOR) and Poole (WAS) briefly engage and disengage off ball after the expiration of the pick.
Flynn (TOR) swipes his hand down and makes contact with Avdija's (WAS) arm that causes him to lose control of the ball.
Siakam (TOR) briefly has his arms around Poole's (WAS) upper half, and marginal contact occurs as Siakam quickly removes his hands.
Flynn (TOR) is moving to align alongside Avdija's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs at the end of Avdija's drive.

Kuzma (WAS) brushes Boucher's (TOR) right shoulder and marginal contact occurs as Boucher elevates for the layup attempt.  Kuzma also avoids making contact with Boucher's head as he contests the shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) is bracing for the contact from Flynn (TOR) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Schroder (TOR) exits the paint within three seconds.
Poole (WAS) keeps his hand on the side of the ball and does not bring part of his hand under the ball in between dribbles.
Siakam (TOR) and Avdija's (WAS) arms become tangled after the release of the shot attempt and marginal contact occurs as they each attempt to establish rebounding position.

Siakam (TOR) brings his off-arm toward Poole's (WAS) front and marginal contact occurs as Poole defends Siakam's drive. Siakam and Poole then make incidental foot contact as Siakam comes to a stop inside the lane.
Poole (WAS) brushes Siakam's (TOR) slightly extended off-arm and marginal contact occurs during Siakam's drive.
Kuzma (WAS) legally contests Siakam's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) brings his hands forward toward Kuzma's (WAS) back and marginal contact occurs as Kuzma receives the pass along the sideline.
Kuzma's (WAS) right foot steps out of bounds after he receives the pass.
Avdija (WAS) and Barnes (TOR) briefly engage and disengage during the inbound, and marginal contact occurs prior to the timeout being awarded to the Raptors.
Kuzma (WAS) briefly grasps Barnes' (TOR) arm and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Kuzma (WAS) commits a take foul on Schroder (TOR).
Barnes (TOR) is moving to Avdija's (WAS) side and marginal contact occurs with Avdija's slightly extended left arm prior to him losing control of the ball near mid-court.
